data.description: Short sale is almost approved! Quick close possible. You'll love this COZY 2 bed plus 1 below, 1 bath BRICK GEORGIAN home in the Brainerd neighborhood of Washington Heights close to park. Home features a nice sized living room, large eat in kitchen with area for entertaining, with central air & forced heat. Finished basement has 1 bedroom and recreational area ready for your creative ideas! Nice sized yard with newer driveway. Close to shopping, schools, train & expressway. Property is a "SHORT SALE" and being SOLD "AS IS"... "SHORT SALE MORTGAGEE'S APPRAISAL IS $175K".  FINAL OFFER PRICE is subject to Bank Approval...
